# RQ-53-10-01-073: Lightning Diverter Strips

## Requirement Statement
The nose cone shall incorporate conductive lightning diverter strips bonded to fuselage structure.

## Acceptance Criteria
- Copper mesh or aluminum strips embedded in composite
- Bonding resistance < 2.5 milliohm
- Current path to fuselage ground plane
- Segmented design to minimize RF interference

## Compliance Status
Design complete, test planned
